headline: Marriott to Report Q4 Earnings: What to Expect From the Stock?
summary: MAR's Q4 results are likely to show improving global demand, solid fee growth and international strength, offset by higher costs and softer incentive fees.

headline: Ahead of Marriott (MAR) Q4 Earnings: Get Ready With Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics

headline: Adam Devine and NFL Stars Join Marriott Bonvoy to Surprise Fans with Riff-Off Inspired Pop-Up Ahead of Super Bowl LX Weekend
summary: Marriott Bonvoy® brought its season-long Keysakes campaign to a showstopping close ahead of Super Bowl LX weekend with a high-energy, musical pop-up featuring Marriott Bonvoy "Fanbassador," Adam Devine and top NFL players at San Francisco's iconic Ferry Building.
